item.title: Glossary
item.description: Glossary Abbreviations Abbreviation Meaning CSO Contour Segmented Objects WEM Winged Edge Meshes GVR Giga Voxel Renderer Filetypes Extension Description of Filetype .mlab Network file, includes all information about the networks modules, their settings, their connections, and module groups. Networks developed by using the MeVisLab SDK are stored as .mlab file and can only be opened having a valid SDK license. .def Module definition file, necessary for a module to be added to the common MeVisLab module database.
